      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEBON DISCO (4) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage third, beaten 3 lengths (23.04) at this track in a Grade 6 over 400m. Makes plenty of appeal. COOL IT MISS (8) ran sixth in a Other last time, copping a check in the run and finishing 6 lengths from the winner over 342m at Angle Park. Has recorded a win from Box 8. Has the ability and can measure up. ETHANOL UNLEADED (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (23.70) last time in a Invitation at this track. Has a good record here including three wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Great chance to atone. CHRISTOFF (5) has strong claims after a long-odds top-three finish last time out.",
